dct_title_s: Manila street : guide to streets, main arteries, tourist spots, embassies, hotels, market places / Philippine Map Co., Inc.
dct_description_sm: Shows municipalities  surrounding Manila City by color coded. Includes indexes to points of interest. Publisher number: P80 Text and location map on verso. Indexed maps on verso: Makati -- Ermita -- Cubao -- Baguio -- Magallanes -- Republic of the Philippines -- Greenhills.
